data.description: Wonderful opportunity to own this condo in the sought-after Woodlake resort like community. This San Mateo Condo features 1 Bedroom, 1 Bathroom, kitchen with granite countertop, tile flooring and stainless-steel appliances, living room and dining room have new carpet and a pleasant view of the greenbelt, updated bathroom with tiled shower, bedroom with large closet and new carpet, outdoor balcony, one reserved parking space, one storage area, Woodlake Community amenities include lake/pond for relaxation, 6 pools, fitness center, clubhouse, tennis courts, hot tub and a convenient laundry area down the hall. Enjoy shopping and dining on Burlingame Avenue and downtown San Mateo, close to Caltrain, Coyote Point Park, Poplar Creek Golf Course, Bay Trail, and Highway 101. Welcome to your new oasis of comfort and convenience. Also nearby are several employment centers such as Gilead Sciences, Sony, Meta Reality Labs, Visa and many more.
